            "stanza_text": "A ce prêtre, voix très lointaine\nPar qui l'office est célébré,\nL'orgue va répondre. Il déchaîne\nD'abord son tumulte sacré."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Tout à coup il s'apaise et prie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Et la foule devant l'autel",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Dans sa mystique rêverie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Croit entendre un écho du ciel.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tout à coup il s'apaise et prie,\nEt la foule devant l'autel\nDans sa mystique rêverie,\nCroit entendre un écho du ciel."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "De nouveau l'effort se rassemble",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "De tous les tuyaux de métal,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Et la cathédrale qui tremble",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "S'emplit d'un fracas musical.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "De nouveau l'effort se rassemble\nDe tous les tuyaux de métal,\nEt la cathédrale qui tremble\nS'emplit d'un fracas musical."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Instrument extraordinaire !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "La nature y met tous ses bruits,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Le sourd grondement du tonnerre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Et le soupir du vent des nuits.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Instrument extraordinaire !\nLa nature y met tous ses bruits,\nLe sourd grondement du tonnerre\nEt le soupir du vent des nuits."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Sous le double clavier d'ivoire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "S'évoque la vie aux cent voix,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Les trompettes de la Victoire",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Comme l'idylle et ses hautbois.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Sous le double clavier d'ivoire\nS'évoque la vie aux cent voix,\nLes trompettes de la Victoire\nComme l'idylle et ses hautbois."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Mais chut !… Le prêtre psalmodie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Devant le tabernacle d'or,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Puis se tait… De flots d'harmonie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "L'orgue inonde l'église encor.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mais chut !… Le prêtre psalmodie\nDevant le tabernacle d'or,\nPuis se tait… De flots d'harmonie\nL'orgue inonde l'église encor."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Et je songe en la nef obscure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Où je priais, distrait un peu :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "C'est la Vie et c'est la Nature",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Répondant aux ordres de Dieu !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et je songe en la nef obscure\nOù je priais, distrait un peu :\nC'est la Vie et c'est la Nature\nRépondant aux ordres de Dieu !"
        }
